Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a task

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in the next release

Name: select_user_story_for_sprint
Description: Whether a user story is pulled into the sprint backlog

Name: team_size
Description: The number of workers in a team

Name: sprint_duration
Description: The planned duration of a sprint in days

Name: worker_availability_percentage
Description: The percentage of time a worker is available

Name: story_point_estimate
Description: The estimated effort for a user story in story points

Name: task_effort_hours
Description: The estimated effort for a task in hours

Name: skill_level
Description: The proficiency level of a worker for a skill

Name: blocker_severity_score
Description: The numerical score representing a blocker's severity
